compexo: ComExpo Cyber Security Foundation is a non-profit organization that believes the Web should be safe, open and equally accessible to everyone. Our motto is to enable people from all age groups and professionals to be a part of making awesome things on the web. We teach all to develop their web literacy skills by spreading awareness and teaching the skills required to develop the web. To do so, we go to school, colleges, offices and any public spaces to teach them about the web.
